Class FakeRegulatedMotor

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.pctest.FakeRegulatedMotor

  • public class FakeRegulatedMotor
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a mock motor for robot-free testing purposes. Use it in place of any instance of a typical lejos motor.
    Author:
    Ryan Au
